overview: Roger Clyne & The Peacemakers throw their own music festival called "Circus Mexicus" and it is Rock & Roll, tacos & tequila all at the beach in Rocky Point, Mexico!  Once a bi-annual event and now annual, the boys were able to capture the fun on this live DVD on the 20th event.  !Viva Circus Mexicus!
title: Circus Mexicus XX
